{"tid":1099712,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：輸0：1好過0：0","createTime":"2019-04-10T03:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T01:51:59.000Z","uid":72652,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d1410e2cdc4e220760f28d89ba0dd5e6e01ca4","tid":1099712,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"曼城首回合敗陣，然而哥迪奧拿正面看落敗，認為輸0:1更勝賽和0:0，此話何解？<br />\n說的，是有更明確目標。哥迪奧拿在球隊周二歐聯8強首回合以0:1受挫於熱刺後說：「戰果令我們次回合處於這個狀況，但有時0:1可能更勝0:0，因為你清楚了解需要做甚麼。」 「在0:0時，你會為進攻或防守心大心細，現在我們知道必需搶攻爭取入球。我們會分析戰果，但我感覺良好，己隊表現好，控制大局，我們擁有機會，並得到12碼，所以這是良好表現。然而是歐聯，那是挑戰。」他續說。 談到射手阿古路射失12碼致敗，哥帥顯然沒怪責之意：「下一次，我們一定取得入球，如今己隊需要備戰水晶宮，沒有時間去想熱刺。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a395a2771cbb453e59b34cf8722da594c3a186","tid":1099712,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3c64ad190ec2d8a640238975dc5d9a9f9a3004","tid":1099712,"uid":15647,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"又黎曼城需要一